Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,======================================== TEXT ========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,明天請各自準備好便當帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,便當？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.27,0:00:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福實訓的校外課程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要求明天一整天都要去附近的山上進行轉運定向越野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,轉運？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,定向越野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了 要好好跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,郊遊♪ 郊遊♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,其他還要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\fs28\fn方正粗圆_GBK\bord0\c&H1C1A2D&\pos(343.385,544.923)\frz9.961}烹飪\N入門
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,轉運定向越野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.78,0:01:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,話說便當用的食材是不是買太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在這座山上有幾個轉運點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(780.308,660)}Power Spot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:02:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,轉運點？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,今天要讓大家到這些地方來積攢運氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,運氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:11.04,Title,,0,0,0,,{@\an8\fs60\c&HA5D662&\fn方正综艺_GBK\pos(640,480)}大家一起去郊遊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,由於讓我一個人來引導不幸的各位會很累
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,於是請了幫手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我是貓尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,今天用金色的轉運模式登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,閃亮亮貓尾草
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是金色為什麼看起來這麼的窮酸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,三倍速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,…我是如此打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾草要是亂動的話你的假面具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,…不是 你的黃金就要掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上就用抽籤來決定出發的順序吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我要抽 我要抽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\fax0.4\fn方正大黑_GBK\fs30\c&H444549&\bord0\pos(814.769,623.692)}倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\fscy105\fax-0.27\fn方正大黑_GBK\fs30\c&H444549&\bord0\frz38.12\pos(891.076,597.845)}第一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你們太不幸了 已經數都不用數了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是在最后里最先出發的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:03:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不出所料是最後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那最後一隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我會在大家後面跟著然後溫暖的守護你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺要糟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我來嘲笑你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,請…等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,兩位 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,現在位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不擅長爬坡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你幫忙揹我的包 真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那倒是沒事 你真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,與其不能加入大家快樂的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,還不如勉強自己參加然後喪命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在這種地方也會有貓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,黑貓 而且還是一群
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}※ 黑貓成群出現和鞋帶突然斷開均為經典的不祥之兆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,鞋帶突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是兩隻鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,鞋帶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就知道會發生這種事所以準備了備用鞋帶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,愛用的茶碗一分為二了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這個也是這個也是這個也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,太不吉利了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真的能轉運嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小雲雀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是雲雀的叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然能在這麼近的地方聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,先不管能不能轉運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,難得來了 就開心的逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是吊橋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,花子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,花子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,輪到我出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是…所謂的年輕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,花子 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,千鈞一髮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你和橋很合不來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,牽起來就不危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真是讓人欣慰的風景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,小牡丹來牽這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,小雲雀真是愛擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要擋著人過橋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是小響和小蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會在我們後面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:06:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 猴子先生會用刀子耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,手真巧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是撿到了誰掉的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不會對蓮起反應也就是說不是雌性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不是傻站著的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,快點跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你們是最後一組
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是遇到什麼不幸的事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不 非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們只是被捲進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這個山丘對面就是第一個轉運點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡一邊積攢運氣一邊吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,掀墊子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,以前我就很想爬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,便當 沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,明明有放進包裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是掉在哪裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,煎蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,花子同學 你要去哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,去找點能吃的野草
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,別
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這是毒草
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那是毒蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,知道得真清楚呢 雲雀同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,因為父母的工作所以稍有瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要吃草了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,來 一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,也請一定要嚐嚐我的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,小響和小蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意的話要不要一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼我們非要在這裡吃不可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 居然用食物來勾引蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,吃這個就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,響特製三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看你們想吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一口都不會分給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,因為剛纔跑過導致味道變得有點奇怪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要一起吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嚐嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我就故意上你一次當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼再來一次「我開動了」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,還能吃很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這隻炸蝦有蝦味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,還有沒有蝦味的炸蝦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我家媽媽會把炸的東西都變成焦炭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,焦炭是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃極了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這個便當真是又可愛又好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今天稍微做的多了點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這份便當是雲雀同學做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我家父母因為工作一直在海外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,料理基本自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼小雲雀家裡只有自己一個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但話說在前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我可沒有感到孤單什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,說明爸爸媽媽肯定是非常信賴小雲雀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟小雲雀能做出這麼好吃的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且今天是大家一起吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就更加好吃了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福實訓可能就是這個目的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡的花田的運氣並不是非常強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,吃過午飯後馬上趕去下一個地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 原來不是啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,補壯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,飯後的是這個 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我去洗下從小雲雀那借的勺子和叉子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,洗… 花子同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這次到我領頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,下一個轉運點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}貓尾草出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是一個更加容易積累運氣的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也該準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 花子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,剛纔說要去洗你借的勺子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,難道！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,花子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,雲雀同學 你那邊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這是花子的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,花子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我攔住花子的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,從以前就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,母親遺傳給我的病弱體質
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,光顧著自己就竭盡全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,說是轉運定向越野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,都是又遲鈍又愚笨又糊塗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,作為人的失敗品的我非要跟來的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一想到花子同學出事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,還不知道是不是出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但畢竟是那個花子同學哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,花子的黴運還挺強的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,黴運？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以肯定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,也許是那麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,求我的話也可以幫你們一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只是被捲進來順帶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去小河下游找找
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,花子她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不 花小泉杏同學不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,花小泉杏同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,午飯後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,說要去洗餐具就再也沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,讓貓尾草去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾草 聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 馬上就去找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你們也去附近找下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子的不幸真不是蓋的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello CQ Hello CQ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是「Kilo India Romeo Alpha Romeo Alpha」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(672,660)}Kirara
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}※ 無線電字母，疑似捏芳文社四格刊《Manga Time Kirara》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有種從未有過的躁動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,今天到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,行蹤不明是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真是個麻煩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,響 不是那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是搞錯方向了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沒怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I Can Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Noooooo！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,花子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好像也不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也去下游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,花子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,花子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,雲雀同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人會在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,雲雀同學的戀人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,戀…戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,還不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:15:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那位所指的箭頭附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,花子同學 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 為什麼會在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一開始是在河邊洗餐具的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,發現髮飾不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在周圍找的時候不小心掉進了河裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒用能抓的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,被河流沖走的同時還被石頭砸到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,還被大魚咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,後來有幾隻猴子先生很友好的向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,然後終於在那裡上岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,比想象中還慘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是個讓人不省心的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,明明響也在到處迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這是外傷藥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,來 請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 小牡丹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去老師那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,說我們棄權
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,身體也暖和起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是用牡丹的藥起效了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,萬一又出現意外情況該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,森林裡的熊先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那種可愛的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼在這裡會有熊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,牡丹 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你們找到花小泉杏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝 比起那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣 我游泳很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾草 在你後面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,先假裝沉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,站著遊喲 厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了 看你後面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是狗刨式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說 好好看後面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 別嚇唬我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾草 有如飛魚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼能限制住熊的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在無線裡聽到有熊從動物園逃出來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:20:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就想著該不會遇上你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 那把槍是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,為了保護你們這樣無比倒黴的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是需要做很多的準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不過還是沒想到會慘成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這個掉在河邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,趁著麻醉藥還有效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我去把這孩子送回動物園
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你們也要像其他人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快點下山哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然發生了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但是玩的很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是沒那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 總是在關鍵的時候派不上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,果然像我這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了牡丹的藥和傘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我們才得救了不是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 小牡丹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,又是雌的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不過聽著鳥鳴聲下山也不壞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要是再有人掉下去或者迷路就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,衝到海里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,喝了好多海水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\an7\fs30}※ 觸摸動物園
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真的非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.82,0:21:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,果然不該選金色的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不過話說回來 那些孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說一個一個運氣都很差
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不過在今天定向越野上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,稍稍轉運一些了呢
